Definition: perennial Eurasian herb with reddish bell-shaped flowers and shining black berries
Example: extensively grown in United States; roots and leaves yield atropine
Synonyms: belladonna_plant, deadly_nightshade, Atropa_belladonna, herbaceous_plant, genus_Atropa, m, perennial, Eurasian, herb, with, reddish, bell-shaped, flowers, and, shining, black, berries, extensively, grown, in, United, States, roots, leaves, yield, atropine
Category: noun.plant
